description:
The cities Sodom and Gomorrah have long lived in infamy, though it is the story of Lot and his family that strikes a cautionary tale. How did the nephew of Abraham end up living there, and what led to his wife turning to a pillar of salt? This biblical story shows us that the decisions that we make today can have huge implications for the future.
